Автор и ведущая - [Елена Ланюгин](/%d0%bf%d1%81%d0%b8%d1%85%d0%be%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%b3%d0%b8%d1%87%d0%b5%d1%81%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%b5-%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%bd%d1%81%d1%83%d0%bb%d1%8c%d1%82%d0%b8%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%b5/%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%b5%d0%bd%d0%b0-%d0%bb%d0%b0%d0%bd%d1%8e%d0%b3%d0%b8%d0%bd%d0%b0/)а